#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:14
msgid ""
"The bounding box is a rectangular box that is wrapped as tightly as "
"possible around the selection. It is oriented parallel to the world "
"axes. In this mode the pivot point lies at the center of the bounding "
"box. You can set the pivot point to *Bounding Box* with :kbd:`Comma` or "
"via the menu in the editor's header. The image below shows how the "
"object's bounding box size is determined by the size of the object."
msgstr ""
"边界框是一个矩形框，在选中项周围尽可能紧密地包裹。方向与世界轴平行。 在此"
"模式下，轴心点位于边界框的中心。可以使用 :kbd:`Comma` 或通过编辑器标题栏"
"中的菜单将轴心点设置为 *边界框中心* 。 下图显示了物体的边界框尺寸是如何由"
"物体的尺寸决定的。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:21
msgid "Relationship between an Object and its Bounding Box."
msgstr "一个物体与其边界框的关系。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:25
msgid "In Object Mode"
msgstr "在物体模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:27
msgid ""
"In *Object Mode*, transformation takes place relative to the location of "
"the objects origin (indicated by the yellow circle), and the size of "
"objects is not taken into account. The image below shows the results of "
"using the *Bounding Box* as the pivot point in a number of situations."
msgstr ""
"在 *物体模式* 中，相对于物体原点(由黄色圆圈表示)的位置进行变换，物体的尺"
"寸则无需考虑。下图显示了在多种情况下使用 *边界框* 作为轴心点的结果。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:35
msgid "Single object rotation."
msgstr "单个物体旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:37
msgid ""
"In this example, the orange rectangle has its origin located on the far "
"left of the mesh, while the blue rectangle has its origin located in the "
"center of the mesh."
msgstr ""
"在此示例中，橙色矩形的原点位于网格的最左侧，而蓝色矩形的原点位于网格的中"
"心。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:40
msgid ""
"When a single object is selected, the rotation takes place around its "
"origin."
msgstr "选择单个物体时，旋转将围绕其原点进行。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:44
msgid ""
"Shows the location of the Bounding Box (left) pivot point compared to "
"the Median Point (right)."
msgstr "显示边界框(左)轴心点与质心点(右)相比较的位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:46
msgid ""
"The image above (left) shows that when multiple objects are selected, "
"the pivot point is calculated based on the bounding box of all the "
"selected objects. More precisely, the centers of objects are taken into "
"account."
msgstr ""
"上图(左)演示了在选中多个物体时，轴心点基于所有选定物体的边界框计算。更为"
"精确的是，物体的中心也被考虑在内。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:52
msgid "In Edit Mode"
msgstr "在编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:54
msgid ""
"This time it is the Object Data that is enclosed in the bounding box. "
"The bounding box in *Edit Mode* takes no account of the Object(s) "
"origins, only the center of the selected vertices."
msgstr ""
"这次它是包含在边界框中的物体数据。 *编辑模式* 中的边界框不考虑物体的原"
"点，仅考虑所选顶点的中心。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:60
msgid ""
"The effects of rotation in different mesh selection modes when the "
"bounding box is set as the pivot point. The pivot point is shown by a "
"yellow circle."
msgstr ""
"将边界框设置为轴心点时，在不同网格选中项模式下旋转的效果。 轴心点用黄色圆"
"圈表示。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:65
msgid "The Bounding Box center compared to the Median Point."
msgstr "边界框中心与质心点相比较。"
